rails g model for doctor, patient and appointment

doctor name, deparment
patient name, age
appointment appointment_datetime:DateTime, t.belongs_to doctor, t.belongs_to patient

doctor has many appointments, patients through appts
patient has many appointments, doctors through appts
appt belongs to doctor and patient

doctor index links to each doctor and shows patient count
doctor show name, department, appoints.each do appt.date, appt.time, patient

patient index links to patient and shows appt count for each
patient show lists all appts with date, time and link_to doctor

appt show date, time, patient and doctor.
NO appt index
